---
import LegalLayout from '../../layouts/LegalLayout.astro';
---

<LegalLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="PatientBillGuide privacy policy — client-side processing, no PHI upload."
  crumbs={[{ label: 'Privacy Policy' }]}
>
  <p><em>Last updated June 2026.</em></p>

  <h2>Summary</h2>
  <p>
    PatientBillGuide tools process bill text and codes <strong>in your browser</strong>. We do
    not require accounts and do not intentionally collect protected health information (PHI)
    through our tools.
  </p>

  <h2>Server logs</h2>
  <p>
    Like most websites, our host may log standard technical data (IP address, browser type,
  pages requested) for security and performance.
  </p>

  <h2>Analytics &amp; advertising</h2>
  <p>
    We may use privacy-conscious analytics and Google AdSense after launch. Third-party
    services have their own policies. We will update this page before enabling ads.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    Questions: <a href="mailto:contact@patientbillguide.com">contact@patientbillguide.com</a> or our
    <a href="/contact/">contact page</a>.
  </p>
</LegalLayout>
